To install xmonad, first install gobject-introspection by pacman.
Then install xmonad, xmonad-contrib and xmonad-utils with pacman.

To install taffybar, install four packages with pacman:

    haskell-gi, haskell-gi-base, haskell-gi-overloading, haskell-gtk

Now clone taffybar and install it with cabal.
